><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6b537c6ab41fa98b4a17f3a3b521ad526dcb9d","tid":2328133,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bef6e4ad7610583c55b42acba5f8b240650895d","tid":2328133,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:29:33.000Z","msg":"我迫不及待好想玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdb7f52cc971a37efd6fef01b48dab04b491de1","tid":2328133,"uid":367485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讓高官先打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5929bab1623eeb7e340c66fb42d2920b02ee37","tid":2328133,"uid":342903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38211b2b8bb89de22a745c6d9ff5e568859fe0dc","tid":2328133,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"立法會一個委員會討論政府防疫措施及疫苗採購事宜，多名議員關注疫苗安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯的蔣麗芸表示，英國免除輝瑞藥廠的法律責任，即使疫苗「出事」亦不用負責，關注本港是否同樣處理，免責後如果「出事」，是否市民自負後果。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，正研究有關問題，因為涉及緊急用途，亦是國際的做法。她又說，如果免除法律責任，本港預先訂購疫苗的藥廠都會採用有關做法。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民的鄭松泰就認為，政府全體高官應先行接種疫苗，一段時間後如果無問題，才討論全民注射。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始回應說，<span class=\"red\">行政長官已表明，如果疫苗到港後會率先接種，又相信市民及高危群組都急不及待希望接種</span>，但她強調任何疫苗都有機會有副作用，市民可選擇是否注射。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565588-20201216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565588-20201216.htm&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE15E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=55bc178f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565588-20201216.htm&h=1ade0d79\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565588-20201216.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"陳無恥可以改名陳離地"},{"pid":"998d661e2fb6703477e646b710e319be81340ffe","tid":2328133,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"777: 我來打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3abdb4d1ac06465d7ed4915befd7454e40f098","tid":2328133,"uid":260251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b88498f99095c02404fc5ed96493fb3a95ebf46","tid":2328133,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e27092a1f46fc5cc654076d546fca71e39f91656","tid":2328133,"uid":76804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4f34c6b7c90933da8c8b621eeb127c709fd0544b","tid":2328133,"uid":30274,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"冇野架<br />\n佢率先接種正版輝瑞嗰款<br />\n賤民咪打支那疫苗<br />\n你冇得揀<br />\n就算比你揀，拎支那貨扮外國貨，鬼分到咩<br />\n港共 sure win"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"其實美國正版輝瑞肯賣比港共咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"一枝半枝點都搵到嘅"}]}